  "prompt": "Where can I download PDF files of Nancy Drew mystery books?",
  "response": "Finding PDF files of Nancy Drew mystery books can be a bit tricky due to copyright laws. Here are some legal and ethical ways to access these books:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Public Domain Resources**\n- Some older Nancy Drew books might be in the public domain (depending on the edition and publication year). Check sites like [Project Gutenberg](https://www.gutenberg.org/) or [Internet Archive](https://archive.org/) for free, legal downloads.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Libraries**\n- Many local libraries offer free access to eBooks, including Nancy Drew titles, through services like **OverDrive** or **Libby**. You\u2019ll need a library card to borrow these books.\n- Some libraries also have PDF versions available for download.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Purchase eBooks**\n- You can buy digital versions of Nancy Drew books from platforms like:\n  - **Amazon Kindle Store**\n  - **Barnes & Noble Nook**\n  - **Apple Books**\n  - **Google Play Books**\n\n---\n\n### **4. Subscription Services**\n- Services like **Scribd** or **Audible** (for audiobooks) offer access to Nancy Drew books for a monthly fee.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Avoid Illegal Downloads**\n- Be cautious of websites offering free PDF downloads of copyrighted books, as these are often illegal and may expose your device to malware.\n\n---\n\nIf you're looking for a specific title, let me know, and I can help guide you further!",
